title: Veeam Backup Server
agents: veeam_rest
catalog: app/veeam
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the Veeam Backup & Replication server information via the REST API.

 It reports:
 - Server name and build version
 - Installed patches
 - Database engine and version (SQL Server or PostgreSQL)
 - Platform information
 - Installation ID

 The check is informational and always returns OK if data is available.

discovery:
 One service is created for the Veeam backup server.
